            <title>[LU-16950] Fix git review branch for b2_15</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16950</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Git review cmd is a very convenient tool for Gerrit review system. We can use &quot;git review -s&quot; to setup remote push url and use &quot;git review&quot; to send patch for review.&lt;/p&gt;

